<br>
I know some people really get joy from making up clever names in-game.  I respect that they do not have the same inclination to actually ‘create a character’ (as opposed to a ‘toon’) in the game as I do.  But in the end, my opinions on names are meaningless: the are rules in the sandbox, and complaining once you finally get caught is just silly.<br>
